va shishada lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik. 10 donadan boshlab. O&#x27;zbekiston bo&#x27;ylab yetkazib berish.</p><a href=\"https://t.me/GraverAdm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition inline-block\">Hisob-kitob olish</a></div></section><section class=\"py-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-12\">O&#x27;ymakorlik uchun materiallar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-teal-500 mb-3\">Metall</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-4\">Zanglamaydigan po&#x27;lat, alyuminiy, guruch. Mukofotlar va biznes-suvenirlari uchun ideal.</p><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Krujkalar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Termoslar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Flesh-disklar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Breloklar</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-teal-500 mb-3\">Yog&#x27;och</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-4\">O&#x27;ymakorlikning iliq effekti bilan tabiiy yog&#x27;och. Premium sovg&#x27;alar uchun.</p><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Ramkalar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Qutichalar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Tagliklar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Daftarlar</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-teal-500 mb-3\">Teri</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-4\">Tabiiy va eko-teri. Shaxsiylashtirilgan biznes aksessuarlari.</p><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Kundaliklar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Hamyonlar</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Vizitka daftarlari</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">✓</span>Kamarlar</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-gray-900/50\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-12\">Qanday ishlashimiz</h2><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 w-12 flex-shrink-0\">01</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Ariza</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Telegram yoki telefon orqali ariza qoldiring</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 w-12 flex-shrink-0\">02</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Bref</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Tafsilotlarni aniqlaymiz: miqdor, material, logotip, muddatlar</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 w-12 flex-shrink-0\">03</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Maket</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Maket tayyorlaymiz va siz bilan kelishamiz</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 w-12 flex-shrink-0\">04</div><div><h3 class=\